{"name":"The Galaxy","permission":{"default":0,"6tM65gLPv3vengSW":3},"flags":{},"content":"<p><strong>What assets does the Enemy use to enforce its power?</strong> Choose three.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Mass incarceration or forced labor. [Name a world notorious for this.]</li>\n<li>Colossal battle stations and warships. [Name the biggest.]</li>\n<li>Strange technological or mystical powers. [What mysterious name identifies these?]</li>\n<li>An elite corps of fearsome warriors. [How do you recognize them?]</li>\n<li>Constraints over interstellar travel. [How do they enforce this?]</li>\n<li>The threat of another enemy or catastrophe. [What&rsquo;s the threat?]</li>\n<li>Subversion of a popular faith. [Name the faith.]</li>\n<li>Economic control and dominance. [Name the economy&rsquo;s most crucial resource.]</li>\n<li>Ubiquitous surveillance and secret police. [What&rsquo;s the slang term for the secret police?]</li>\n<li>Manipulation of truth, facts, and public opinion. [Name one important lie.]</li>\n<li>Feuding among lesser powers. [Name a world these powers are squabbling over.]</li>\n<li>Public apathy, ignorance, or despair. [What influence keeps people out of the fight?]</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What leaders control the Enemy&rsquo;s power?</strong> Choose one option, and then name them.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>A charismatic dictator. [What&rsquo;s their best-loved slogan?]</li>\n<li>A terrifying despot. [What&rsquo;s their favorite act of cruelty?]</li>\n<li>A devious puppet master. [Who do they stand behind?]</li>\n<li>Several independent rivals. [How many? Two? Four? Twelve? Only name one of them to start with.]</li>\n<li>A secret cabal. [What symbol, mask, or communication method do their underlings recognize them by?]</li>\n<li>A hostile and unfathomable intelligence. [Where did it come from? A lab? Another galaxy?]</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What do the Enemy&rsquo;s common footsoldiers look like?</strong> Choose one option.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Uniformed soldiers. [What&rsquo;s striking about their uniforms?]</li>\n<li>Emotionless robots. [What phrase do they use most often?]</li>\n<li>Savage creatures. [What terrifying noise do they make?]</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What are the Enemy&rsquo;s most notable misdeeds?</strong> Choose three.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Strips inhabited worlds of a specific resource. [Water? Gold? Helium-3? Blood? Dreams? Other?]</li>\n<li>Ignores suffering from corruption and chaos. [Name an exceptionally corrupt or lawless place.]</li>\n<li>Indoctrinates the powerless or gullible into loyal service. [What incentive does the Enemy offer?]</li>\n<li>Pursues morally questionable scientific developments. [What are they researching now?]</li>\n<li>Encourages compliance through outrageous acts of cruelty. [Name a recent despicable act.]</li>\n<li>Constructs colossal monuments to its own glory. [What are they building now?]</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What assets does the Resistance have?</strong> Choose three.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>An organized military force. [Name it, and one of their strongholds.]</li>\n<li>Disorganized bands of outlaws and malcontents. [Name the most notorious band.]</li>\n<li>A small enlightened utopia beyond the Enemy&rsquo;s reach. [Name it. What&rsquo;s one amazing thing there?]</li>\n<li>A wise, inspiring leader. [Name them. What were they before joining the Resistance?]</li>\n<li>A dispersed and secretive conspiracy. [Name them and one rumor of their origins or abilities.]</li>\n<li>People of conscience within the Enemy&rsquo;s service. [Name one and decide what they do for the Resistance.]</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Finally, what do we call the Enemy?</strong></p>","_id":"c8vpTxD5T88TtdmT"}
{"name":"A Location","permission":{"default":0,"6tM65gLPv3vengSW":3},"flags":{},"content":"<h1>Purpose</h1>\n<p>What was this location prepared for, or what do people use it for?</p>\n<h1>Appearance</h1>\n<p>What does this place look like, broadly speaking?</p>\n<h1>Surroundings</h1>\n<p>What&rsquo;s nearby?</p>\n<h1>Features</h1>\n<p>What will the heroes find here? If this is a building, what important rooms or facilities does it contain? If this is a city, what neighborhoods or structures are significant?</p>","_id":"yMca9rLf3aQzEwlN"}
